### 2. Create Wallet (Protected, requires token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": "your-user-id-here",
  "tag": "Main Wallet",
  "chainId": "your-chain-id-here",
  "address": "0x1234...abcd"
}

### 3. Get All Wallets (Protected, requires token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get Wallet by ID (Protected, requires token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallets/your-wallet-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Update Wallet (Protected, requires token)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/wallets/da46a7a6-d343-4f3d-8c53-1a6433caa7e2
